org.apache.iotdb.tsfile.encoding.encoder

Class Encoder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.iotdb.tsfile.encoding.encoder.Encoder
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BitmapEncoder, DeltaBinaryEncoder, FloatEncoder, GorillaEncoder, PlainEncoder, RegularDataEncoder, RleEncoder

    public abstract class Encoder
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is the parent class of all Encoders. Every encoder has a specific <encoderType> which represents the type of this encoder
